sections.heading: Retirement accounts6-574.Retirement accountsA credit union may act as trustee or custodian of any form of retirement, pension, profit sharing or deferred income accounts for its members, pension funds of self-employed individuals eligible for membership and pension funds of a company or organization
sections.text: Retirement accounts6-574.Retirement accountsA credit union may act as trustee or custodian of any form of retirement, pension, profit sharing or deferred income accounts for its members, pension funds of self-employed individuals eligible for membership and pension funds of a company or organization whose employees or members are eligible for membership in the credit union.
